Note: Symbol Resolution Tests
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "test_linker_has_symbol" that takes results as Integer returns Integer:
    T.begin_suite(results, "linker_has_symbol")

    Let ctx be Linker.create_linker_context()
    T.assert_not_null(results, "linker context created", ctx)

    Note: Initially no symbols
    Let has_any be Linker.linker_has_symbol(ctx, "anything")
    T.assert_equal(results, "no symbols initially", has_any, 0)

    Note: Null context should return 0
    Let null_result be Linker.linker_has_symbol(0, "test")
    T.assert_equal(results, "null context returns 0", null_result, 0)

    Note: Null name should return 0
    Let null_name be Linker.linker_has_symbol(ctx, 0)
    T.assert_equal(results, "null name returns 0", null_name, 0)

    Return 1
End Process

